dct_title_s: Map of the peninsula of Florida and adjacent islands, Florida East Coast Railway
dct_description_sm: Shows railroad lines, major cities, traveler information, and township boundaries.; Insets: Map of Florida and the West Indies -- Bahama Islands -- Map of Cuba showing its proximity to Key West, Florida, the southern terminus of the Florida East Coast Railway ...
